  m_Name: Bronze Kobolds
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  workshopItem:
    publishedFileId: 0
    visibility: 3
    tags: 29
    loadPriority: 0
    previewSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 27712d2f9bbe5b64baceb5004c158549, type: 3}
    language: 0
    title: Safeq's collection of Kobolds
    description: 'Here''s the kobolds I''ve been working on for some years now.

      Includes:

      Kobold+
      (Bronze)

      Kobold^ (Super Bronze)

      Kobold++ (Silver)

      Kobold^^
      (Super Silver)

      Kobold+++ (Gold)

      Kobold^^^ (Super Gold)

      Kobold++++
      (Obsidian)

      Kobold^^^^ (Super Obsidian)

      Kobold+++++ (Rainbow Opal)

      Kobold^^^^^
      (Super Rainbow Opal)

      KoboldRose (Rose/Mermaid)

      Kobold# (Alexandrite/Galaxy)

      Cowbold
      (Cow Hide)

      KoboldAmethyst (Eggplant )

      KoboldCitrine (Pineapple)

      KoboldEmerald
      (Melon)

      KoboldTopaz (Banana)

      (replace Kobold with Egg/Heart to
      get the respective Egg/Heart. Amethyst, Citrine, Emerald & Topaz)


      There''s
      also the:

      Dlobok (Kobold spelled backwards)

      Gge (Egg backwards)

      and
      Treah (Heart backwards)

      gives those a try!


      I''ve also made Ovispots
      for each kobolds so players can spawn in any character naturally instead of
      using cheats.'
    changeNotes: Released
    guid: 595fd085-05c3-499c-aaab-834a45697eff
